examples.en: His sermons were full of puns and conceits.

examples.en: His sermons were unpredictably witty and satirical as well as eloquent.

examples.en: His sermons were all bolstered up with Greek and Latin.

examples.en: When you hear his sermons, you will be able to believe, too
